<h4 id="6-可选链">6. 可选链</h4>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>// 可选链，方法可能会不被调用
delegate?.callback()

let str: String? = "Never say never"
